Description: IDE for the B method and Event-B
 Atelier B is an integrated development environment for the B method. It
 supports writing B and Event-B models, type-checking, proof obligation
 generation, and automatic and interactive provers.
 .
 This package repackages the Atelier B Community Edition, proprietary freeware
 distributed by CLEARSY, from the upstream vendor package for Ubuntu.
